Text: Starts in the middle of a fight, but since it's the only download there seems to be of the facebook fights....worth it.

If you really want to see the Prelims, don't download this version. This starts part of the way through a fight, I'm not even sure if it's the first one; one thing you will notice is that there is no commentary for a while, it also pauses from time to time, and for the last 13 minutes or so, all you get is this:
http://bayimg.com/JaEpmAAEa

As said starts in the middle of the fight, there's only 3 fights (well 2 1/2) and duration is 57 mins with last 7-10 mins of end screen (thank you for watching blah, blah...) If I knew I'd definitely download different torrent. Other than that A 9 V 9
And plus no commentary for a while plus it freezes in the middle of the fights for like 10 secs...
Yes, this is rubbish, starts half way through a fight and no commentary at all. Disappointed, expected better from scene4all. Have deleted.
